title: Sawbones: Rock Medicine
description:
This week on Sawbones, we'll meet a San Francisco doctor that reimagined how we care for people with drug addiction and got a hit put out on himself in the process.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
